{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976600/extras/AboutThisGameGif.gif?t=1721339535\" /><br>Deathland Drifters is a 1-6 player co-op roguelike about piloting a hovership across a doomed alien planet. An endless rain of space debris has shattered civilization on this once thriving colony world and transformed it into a hellscape. Your crew of Drifters are stranded on this desolate planet, but one spaceship, miraculously intact, could be your last shot at escape.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976600/extras/UniqueBuildsGif.gif?t=1721339535\" /><br>As you fight your way through handcrafted environments, you can scavenge loot to upgrade your ship and weapons, creating unique builds for each run. Each weapon has a unique upgrade tree, and randomized loot can be combined to create unique builds for your ship!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976600/extras/SoloOrCoopGIF.gif?t=1721339535\" /><br>Pick the hovership that best suits your playstyle and needs! Most hoverships can accommodate up to 6 players, but a select few compact hoverships are specially designed for 1-2 players.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976600/extras/UnlockableShipsGIFv2.gif?t=1721339535\" /><br>Each hovership has its own set of weapons, abilities, and playstyles. Create different layouts or unlock new hoverships to keep every run fresh and entertaining.","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2976600?t=1721339535","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2976600?t=1721339535","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976600/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1721339535","capsule_imagev5":"https://sh